trans-unit.source: Runs a set of child activities according to a single defined ordering.
trans-unit.target: Executa um conjunto de filho atividades de acordo com uma única ordem definida.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] The SequenceActivity is a <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity>, meaning the SequenceActivity can contain other activities.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]É o SequenceActivity um <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity>, que significa que o SequenceActivity pode conter outras atividades.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity>

trans-unit.source: The SequenceActivity class coordinates the running of a set of child activities in an ordered manner, one at a time.
trans-unit.target: A classe SequenceActivity coordena a execução de um conjunto de atividades filho de forma ordenada, um por vez.

trans-unit.source: The SequenceActivity is completed when the final child activity is finished.
trans-unit.target: O SequenceActivity é concluída quando a atividade filho final é concluída.

trans-unit.source: Classes that derive from SequenceActivity should not implement the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.IActivityEventListener%601> interface, or the derived class will not execute correctly.
trans-unit.target: Classes que derivam de SequenceActivity não devem implementar o <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.IActivityEventListener%601>interface ou classe derivada não serão executados corretamente.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.IActivityEventListener%601>
